:: 1
"Alright! I got this, I found a new cave that's not in my maps, Adventure awaits!" said Lyara as she entered the cave, ready to explore the unknowness of the cave and bring with her knowledge and treasure.She already imagines herself back in the guild showing of her new discoveries and treasures, she would be the talk of the town! "I'll show Bardus that I am a worthy element in their guild!"- Lyara said as she moved forward towards some stairs leading down.
[[Continue->A]]

:: 2
After Climbing a set of stairs Lyara finds herself at where she was first when she started descending the cave stairs"This was incredible" Said Lyara as she starts running towards town ready to tell the tales of her adventurein the unknown cave. "I'm sure they will name the cave my name after hearing my tales!" Thought Lyara
THE END.

:: A
Lyara found an uncharted cave and eagerly explored it, imagining sharing her findings with Bardus.
[[I'll prove my worth to the guild.->B]]
[[To Bardus first or secrets of the past?->C]]

:: B
'To the unseen depths or ancient secrets.'
[[Continue->E]]

:: C
Lyara spent hours studying the enigmatic symbols etched into stone tablets within a secluded alcove. As she traced her fingers over their patterns, an unexpected sense of kinship with history washed over her.
[[Continue->I]]

:: D
Filled with newfound knowledge and stories to share about Eldoria's ancient past rather than treasures found alone in the cave, Lyara ran towards Irinu town. As she entered Bardus guild hall amid cheers for 'Lyra', they gathered around her not only admiringly but also intrigued by tales of history beyond their village.
[[Continue->2]]

:: E
Deep in the caverns, Lyara discovered runes etched on stone walls that seemed to pulse with a faint glow.
[[Enter the cave's secret chambers (max. words: 'Discover hidden passages')->F]]
[[Follow the glowing runes (max. words: 'Trace history's path')->G]]

:: F
Inside a chamber lined with ancient artifacts, Lyara uncovers an old map that points to other parts of Eldoria.
[[Continue->H]]

:: G
The trail leads back through secret passages beneath Maralus Hill, culminating at a forgotten part of Irinu where echoes of ancient Eldorians still whisper.
[[Continue->H]]

:: H
Filled with newfound knowledge and stories to share about Eldoria's ancient past rather than treasures found alone in the cave, Lyara ran towards Irinu town. As she entered Bardus guild hall amid cheers for 'Lyra', they gathered around her not only admiringly but also intrigued by tales of history beyond their village.
