:: I
Lyara felt a wave of memories washing over her. She saw the memories of a mage from a distant time, learning the lost history that once befell in the nearby land.
[[Choose wisdom over wealth->J]]
[[Seek connection with history->K]]

:: J
Narrative for node B with details about ancient Eldoria and the symbols' significance.
