:: K
Alternate outcome where Lyara felt more connected to a mysterious figure in the cave, leading her on a small exploratory journey within it that ended without revealing any treasures but rather historical insights.
[[Continue->U]]

:: L
Narrative for node D linking back to Node 2 with excitement about sharing newfound knowledge and stories of Eldoria's ancient past instead of personal discovery alone in the cave, leading Lyara straight into Irinu town where she is celebrated by her guild mates ready to listen.
