:: M
Lyara stood at the entrance to a hidden cavern beneath Eldoria's hills, drawn here by legends of untold riches.
[[Explore Ancient Artifacts in Irinu->N]]
[[Discover Treasures Beneath Maralus->O]]

:: N
Navigating deeper into the shadows of this forgotten passageway, Lyara discovered ancient symbols etched into cold stone walls — a testament to Eldoria's enigmatic past.
[[Continue->Q]]

:: O
The glow from the wall catches her eye. She realizes these markings are not just art; they tell stories of old, hinting at Eldoria's ancient secrets and forgotten gods.
[[Continue->P]]

:: P
Eager to share tales with Bardus mates in Irinu town.
[[Continue->L]]

:: Q
Lyara, heart pounding, traced the symbols and uncovered an arcane inscription that whispered of hidden chambers beneath Maralus Hill.
[[Venture to Eldoria's secret caverns->R]]
[[Seek out Maralus Hill secrets->S]]

:: R
Racing back through Irinu towards home with tales from her daring exploration, Lyara felt a sense of accomplishment and belonging amongst the Bardus guild members.
[[Continue->T]]

:: S
Lyara delved into another concealed chamber where she stumbled upon an enchanted harp that played melodies aligning with her thoughts. The music seemed to imbue her spirit, revealing visions of Eldoria's glorious history and ancient civilizations.
[[Continue->T]]

:: T
Returned from either quest into Irinu town feeling fulfilled in both adventures
