:: Z
Lyara senses the mysterious watcher and decides to investigate quietly without revealing her presence. She finds an old book detailing legends about Eldoria's history, hinting at secrets yet uncovered.
[[Continue->AB]]

:: AA
To Lyara's surprise, the figure approaches with a welcoming smile and introduces himself as Elrond. He shares his knowledge of Eldoria's past heroes who once protected this secret cave from evil forces.
[[Continue->AB]]

:: AB
